// Kernel entry point. `open use "../kernel/prelude.disp"` brings the full
// surface: substrate combinators, substrate utils, and the new two-Σ-op
// kernel + library types (lib/kernel/core.disp). The legacy 7-primitive
// kernel (handlers/walker) and lib/types/ were retired in the NEXT cutover.

open use "../prelude.disp"
open use "utils.disp"
open use "core.disp"
